title: Robert Jordan - Knife of Dreams 1.2 (HTML, Wheel of Time 11)
description:
Book 11 in Robert Jordan's "Wheel of Time" fantasy book series.

I converted this to HTML from a PDF I found, to be able to use it with my e-book reader. The PDF had hard line-breaks, so the paragraph division is guesstimated, but it seems to have worked rather well.

In this version, 1.2, I've also fixed quite a lot of OCR errors and added some section breaks.
